Name: Nothing to God
About the game: You are a being created from the God of Nothing, born without a name and referred to only as a “husk”. Sent to acquire the blessings of the gods, you must persevere against the many challenges they present to you. Whether they are angry, complacent, or indifferent, you mustn’t waver from your duty, lest you find yourself as an abandoned corpse that none shall remember. Dodge a multitude of intricate patterns as you delve deeper into the secrets of universe, recieving blessings so that you may become something more. When all is said and done, what will you become? Features: -Bullet-dodging! -Pixel art! -Optional checkpoints! -Practice mode! -A storyline that is, quite frankly, edgy. -All developed by one person!
